VERIFICATION
<section>
<h2>How to Verify Even</h2>
<div class="privacy-section">
<h3>1. Browser Development Tools</h3>
<ol style="color: #555; margin: 1em 0; padding-left: 2em;">
<li>Open the <strong>Development tools</strong> (F12 or Cmd+Option+I)</li>
<li>Go to the tab <strong>Network</strong> (Network)</li>
<li>Enter a test password in Time2Crack</li>
<li>Watch network queries: you won't see <strong>that</strong> HiBP request with 5-char prefix</li>
<li>The full password does not appear <strong>Never</strong> in requests</li>
</ol>
</div>
<div class="privacy-section">
<h3>2. See source code</h3>
<ul style="color: #555; margin: 1em 0; padding-left: 2em;">
