<li>The code contains <strong>zero external dependencies</strong> — it's pure JavaScript</li>
<li>You can inspect <code>app.js</code> and verify that:
            <ul style="margin-top: 0.5em;">
<li>Passwords are always local</li>
<li>Only the HiBP 5-char prefix is sent</li>
<li>No tracking cookie or personal analytics</li>
</ul>
</li>
</ul>
</div>
<div class="privacy-section">
<h3>3. Test in offline mode</h3>
<ul style="color: #555; margin: 1em 0; padding-left: 2em;">
